description: Demolition of 2-6 Hardwicks Way including the former Litten Tree public house, part demolition and erection of 6 storey extension to 127-129 Wandsworth High Street and erection of new buildings fronting Buckhold Road and Hardwicks Way between 4 and 10 storeys in height. Developmnent comprises Classes A1 (retail), A3 (food and drink) and B1 (office) uses at ground floor level with 138 flats above (including 35 affordable flats), the creation of public open space, and associated basement car parking.
